title: Rifftrax Presents :Star Wars V - The Empire Strikes Back
description:
RIFFTRAX PRESENTS:

Star Wars V : The Empire Strikes Back

Featuring:
Mike Nelson, Kevin Murphy, Bill Corbett & Special Guest Star Chad Vader

The Rifftrack and film audio track was synced in Cubase SX3 and sidechain compression was applied using Waves C1. The compression settings were according to Rifftrax standards, which is as follows:

Threshold: -50
Ratio: 1.5:1
Attack: 9.99ms
Release: 485ms
Knee: 25.5

Original video rip by K3LtZ - Thanks, this would not have been possible without your help. Great rip! I did my best to preserve the integrity of the rip by encoding it with DivX 6.8.5 Codec, with Quality to 10 and a 1-pass rate control @ 730.467 kbps. No resize or format conversion. Rendered out of Sony Vegas Pro 8.
